data.description: As of 11/09 Update: Seller will be paying the Solar System at Closing. ( 25K) Welcome to this inviting, well maintained home in the gated community of Windsor Park. This beautiful home has three spacious bedrooms, two bathrooms, and an open floor plan ready for you to move in. This home's features include a large living room with a gas insert fireplace, an open kitchen with new stainless steel appliances, vaulted ceilings in the master bedroom and living room. This master suite is very large and features a walk-in closet. The neighborhood amenities include pool and spa as well as landscaping in common areas. This home is situated in the award winning Clovis School District.
